name: Everything In The Kitchen Sink
description:
Everything is going into the portal. A time portal has opened. The Entity searches for something -- someone. The Entity is an AI from a future beyond the human apocalypse. More at https://bit.ly/sageAnomaly

This was created from an edited image from an artist Bembo Davis (https://twitter.com/BemboDavis) on Twitter who put green blobs on a Craigslist posting.
